# Work machine: Quadro P4000/P2000 (Pascal) + RDP access from locked-down
# Windows clients (mstsc is often the only allowed client there).

# --- GPU: Pascal needs the legacy 580xx branch (last to support it) ---
nvidia-580xx-dkms
nvidia-580xx-utils
linux-cachyos-headers

# --- RDP session stack (xrdp serves an XFCE/X11 session; Wayland can't do RDP) ---
xorg-server
xorg-xinit
xfce4
